*This code will add a footer to you webpage*
*You can use images or text*
*Make sure you link you css pages to your html files*
*Paste the code bellow into a css file*
.social-icons {
  text-align: center;
  }  
.social-icons li {
  display:inline-block;
  list-style-type:none;
  }
.social-icons li a {
  border-bottom: none;
  }
.social-icons li img {
  width:30px;
  height:30px;
  margin-right: 20px;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: gray;
   color: #ffffff;
   text-align: center;
}

*Paste the code bellow at the bottom of your html file*
*For a image remove the If text put here*
*For text remove the <img src='path to image' />*
*You can add as many sections to your footer*

<ul class="social-icons">
    <li><a href="Paste link here"><img src='If image path to image' />If text put text</a></li>
</ul>
</footer>
